# Title: Split A File Into Pieces - Linux
# Author: Igor Fits, oscd.community
# Date: 2020-10-15
# Level: low
# Description: Detection use of the command "split" to split files into parts and possible transfer.
# MITRE Tactic: Exfiltration
# Tags: attack.exfiltration, attack.t1030
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/linux/auditd/syscall/lnx_auditd_split_file_into_pieces.yml
# False Positives:
#   - Legitimate administrative activity

comm="split" type="SYSCALL"